{
  "stem": "24466.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have to go through [NON-ENGLISH], where other partisans were, the Russian partisans, Ludowa, Krajowa, Armia Krajowa, Ludowa, Jewish partisans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have to go through them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was very, I would say, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] dangerous.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On-- on horses and only at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And wherever you're assigned during the day, that was already arranged.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some arrangements was done-- it was-- it took us five nights to go there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Five nights.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We came over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We stayed there two days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the commandant from there sent us back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The same-- to go back to-- to-- to [NON-ENGLISH], to where from we came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No reasons, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Came back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I believe the commandant from [INAUDIBLE] was frightened that something will happen to us, and he's-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and he's-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he sent us out to get rid of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, on the way there going through the all other partisans, that they will finish us off, and he will not be responsible for [INAUDIBLE] because he was his head.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was frightened for him, because he's in the scene.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he has to look after us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't kill them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That didn't happen in-- in-- amongst us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That happens on the way when he was going-- and the other sent us back to-- to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "True, that, in that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the south of [NON-ENGLISH], a lot of Jews from Warsaw have been there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In partisan groups.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that partisan group.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wouldn't have talked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't went-- they didn't talk a Jew-- like a Jew to a Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, partisan?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where from?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I know who was a Jew and who wasn't a Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could find.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
